match Globals.talkCutscene:
	when 0:
		[speed=0.2]They seem to put something into their pocket
		Captor: [speed=2]Captor: [speed=0.2]You know, this could be a lot easyer if you where to just talk.
		Captor: [speed=2]Captor: [speed=0.2]But oh well, maybe a few more days will do the trick.
		[speed=0.2]They leave the room
	when 1:
		[speed=0.2]They read a note that was on the table
		Captor: [speed=2]Captor: [speed=0.2]Right, almost forgot about that...
		Captor: [speed=2]Captor: [speed=0.2]I will be out for a bit today, don't try anything funny.
		Captor: [speed=2]Captor: [speed=0.2]You know what the consequenses are...
		[speed=0.2]They leave the room
	when 2:
		Captor: [speed=2]Captor: [speed=0.2]GODDAMNIT...
		[speed=0.2]They turn to you seeming irritated
		Captor: [speed=2]Captor: [speed=0.2]I have to go, you better not try anything!
		[speed=0.2]They quickly leave the room

