[speed=0.2]Then a butterfly shows up
[speed=0.2]It hovers near you for a moment
[speed=0.2]Butterfly: [speed=2]Voice: [speed=0.2]Hey, you need some help?
[speed=0.2]You look around confused for a moment
[speed=0.2]Butterfly: [speed=2]Voice: [speed=0.2]*sighs* It is me, the butterfly
[speed=0.2]You look to the butterfly again
[speed=0.2]Butterfly: [speed=2]Butterfly: [speed=0.2]well, do you want some help?
[speed=0.2]You nod quickly
[speed=0.2]Butterfly: [speed=2]Butterfly: [speed=0.2]I can send you back in time
[speed=0.2]Butterfly: [speed=2]Butterfly: [speed=0.2]There you can change some small things around
[speed=0.2]Butterfly: [speed=2]Butterfly: [speed=0.2]Maybe that will change your fate

=> END